snippet.title: First ZooRacers Beta Live Action!
snippet.description:
Watch the ZOO Team battling against each other for the first time on ZooRacers Beta!

Stay tuned to our socials for upcoming Public Beta release!

✔ ZooGames Protocol - https://Zoo.Games

📢 Keep up with all ZooEcosystem news via Twitter - https://twitter.com/ZooEcosystem
🔎 Read our numerous informative articles on the ZooEcosystem blog - https://blog.Zoo.One

💡 Join our great ZooKeeper and OpenZoo community on Telegram - https://t.me/ZooEcosystem
🐵 Join us on the ZooEcosystem Discord: https://discord.gg/ZooEcosystem
